  "detailed_description": "<h1>Consider Kill It With Fire</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Shoot baddies. Dodge Bullets. Find Secrets</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/9b649bac336d9c9a996be7c1494320c4.poster.avif?t=1727200331\" width=256 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/9b649bac336d9c9a996be7c1494320c4.webm?t=1727200331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/9b649bac336d9c9a996be7c1494320c4.mp4?t=1727200331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/b7f12310de11031bba07795d70c112ff.poster.avif?t=1727200331\" width=256 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/b7f12310de11031bba07795d70c112ff.webm?t=1727200331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/b7f12310de11031bba07795d70c112ff.mp4?t=1727200331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sequel to the most adorable First Person Shooter Gun Ballet. Feel the speed once again as you jump and shoot your way through the familiar cuetsy abstract world filled with clever traps and angry baddies fuming with rage. Pick out targets with precision accuracy and dodge an infinite barrage of bullets carefully jumping between floating islands all while racing the clock for a better score.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/f815de5d53a147cf65237bdcd4290698.poster.avif?t=1727200331\" width=256 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/f815de5d53a147cf65237bdcd4290698.webm?t=1727200331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/f815de5d53a147cf65237bdcd4290698.mp4?t=1727200331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/f4ad384cb22757035d8572b813fea908.poster.avif?t=1727200331\" width=256 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/f4ad384cb22757035d8572b813fea908.webm?t=1727200331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/f4ad384cb22757035d8572b813fea908.mp4?t=1727200331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play a 100+ levels of pure jumping and shooting<br></li><li>Experience five unique worlds with brand new traps and enemies<br></li><li>Replay every level in a more challenging new game mode ☯<br></li><li>Explore to find hidden levels, secrets and achievements<br></li><li>Vibe to an original soundtrack by Calum Bowen</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019590/extras/7147b7168b7b03bfe876f57fcb4bd162.avif?t=1727200331\" width=640 height=140 /></span>",
